{"tid":1180764,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超認有內地執法人員不依法律 辯稱：中國都係講緊依法治國","createTime":"2019-06-01T05:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-01T05:52:56.000Z","uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3ed1a64a7c4a23ef40ddb64b0580e8e4862edb5b","tid":1180764,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:49:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190601/large/1559364154_0bba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190601%2Flarge%2F1559364154_0bba.jpg&h=dcfd1845&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多名議員繼續對內地司法不公情況，對引渡提出質疑。民主黨林卓廷指，內地實行「黨管幹部」原則，內地司法人員身分為公務員，受中共管轄，質疑港府如何確保移交疑犯後獲公平審訊。李家超反駁林斷章取義，辯稱「國家都係講緊依法治國」，雖然在執法過程，內部可能有某階層的執法人員未依法律，他又引述內地的刑法條文，稱有關當局可獨立行使執法權及檢察權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190601/59664703\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190601%2F59664703&d=RSiYdbgXC1SHA4i8VFLgbbXdyKWV89KwSxbYnQ5zRIM%3D&h=ebf101f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190601%2F59664703&h=0aa46c39\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190601/59664703</a>"},{"pid":"7d3cf95dd28ef2f48bdab8a6346da469ced0d656","tid":1180764,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-01T05:50:45.000Z","msg":"仲話引渡犯會有無罪推定同有基本人權 真係搞笑 會唔會為左個別幾個犯而改變成個制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ec6464486d2cdf6a00142749166ad4a6751e209","tid":1180764,"uid":231102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":